\end_inset

 存在且等于 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{\Omega}g\,\phi=(-1)^{|\underline{\alpha}|}\int_{\Omega}(\underline{\partial}^{\underline{\alpha}}\phi)\,f,\quad\forall\phi\in D(\Omega)
\]

\end_inset

等价于 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{\partial}^{\underline{\alpha}}F=G$
\end_inset

。
